race.comment: BROCKY SANDS (7) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 3.5 lengths third over 510m this track in 29.20. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can go on with it. MAGICAL PAWS (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (29.48) in a Grade 5 at this track. Bold showing expected. MADALIA SNOOPY (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (30.04) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Must be included in calculations. MR. PRESIDENT (8) looks an each-way chance. Something for the Multiples: UNLEASH ZAC (5)
